### Hooks Cleanup

The [useInterrogationLog.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/lib/hooks/useInterrogationLog.ts) and [useNotes.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/lib/hooks/useNotes.ts) hook files will be **kept** in the codebase (not deleted) since they may be referenced elsewhere or useful in the future. Only their usage in the modified components will be removed.

